      <p>The Bikevertising Company turned Out Of Home advertising into a dynamic industry by using bikes as an advertising space. By offering the billboard bikes to students and young professionals free of charge, they ensure movement throughout the day. I offered to try my hand at motion graphics to visualize the potential daily reach and full coverage of a city with hundreds of these billboard bikes. After Effect's rather steep learning curve proved to be a great challenge.</p>

      <p>The result was part of a more extensive video showcasing the full scope of Bikevertising's services.</p>

